  <text>
    <body>
      <ab type="lido:objectWorkType">Photograph</ab>
      <ab subtype="creation" type="lido:event">
        <date>1954</date>
      </ab>
      <ab type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">At its centre, the photograph features two actors in traditional Albanian costume and a man in black clothes holding an unidentifiable object in his right hand. A film camera and cameraman are positioned in the bottom right corner. A sunshade protrudes into the picture.</ab>
      <ab subtype="comment" type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">‘Skenderbeu’ was a Soviet feature with Albanian contribution. It was released in 1954 and directed by Sergei Yutkevich. The Russian film title was ‘Velikiy voin Albanii Skanderbeg’ (‘Великий воин Албании Скандербег‘).</ab>
